1
00:00:06,089 --> 00:00:08,514
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,514 --> 00:00:12,169
♫  Time has bear witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,169 --> 00:00:18,362
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,362 --> 00:00:24,588
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,588 --> 00:00:30,909
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,909 --> 00:00:35,995
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:35,995 --> 00:00:43,295
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,295 --> 00:00:48,319
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,319 --> 00:00:49,932
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,932 --> 00:00:55,695
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,695 --> 00:01:02,095
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:02,095 --> 00:01:07,962
♫  With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:07,962 --> 00:01:11,747
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:28,622 --> 00:01:30,541
He's not picking up, huh?

15
00:01:42,502 --> 00:01:44,334
It's from Gao Bin.

16
00:01:45,741 --> 00:01:47,580
Do you want to answer it?

17
00:01:56,201 --> 00:01:57,962
The number you have dialed is powered off.

18
00:01:57,962 --> 00:02:00,121
Sorry...

19
00:02:00,121 --> 00:02:02,118
He turned if off.

20
00:02:02,118 --> 00:02:04,162
Well, what should we do?

21
00:02:04,162 --> 00:02:06,661
Stay calm. Let me figure it out.

22
00:02:08,441 --> 00:02:10,561
Who can we call besides Anna?

23
00:02:10,561 --> 00:02:12,478
Her Third Uncle.

24
00:02:12,478 --> 00:02:15,281
Her Third Uncle won't know for sure.

25
00:02:16,381 --> 00:02:19,122
Hai... Hai...

26
00:02:21,101 --> 00:02:23,357
Zhan Chonghai.

27
00:02:29,141 --> 00:02:31,098
I don't have his number.

28
00:02:31,622 --> 00:02:33,312
The business card.

29
00:02:38,701 --> 00:02:40,333
Read it for me.

30
00:02:41,402 --> 00:02:43,761
- 139...
- 139...

31
00:02:43,761 --> 00:02:47,322
- 6967...
- 6697...

32
00:02:47,322 --> 00:02:49,381
6967!

33
00:02:51,462 --> 00:02:55,162
6.. 6..

34
00:03:05,581 --> 00:03:06,981
Hello, who is this?

35
00:03:06,981 --> 00:03:08,182
Gao Bin.

36
00:03:08,182 --> 00:03:10,342
Bin, what's wrong?

37
00:03:10,342 --> 00:03:14,762
Let me ask you something. Is Gao Yang with you guys right now?

38
00:03:20,241 --> 00:03:21,622
Say something!

39
00:03:21,622 --> 00:03:23,902
I'm telling you. Gao Yang went missing.

40
00:03:23,902 --> 00:03:26,661
If you don't say anything, I'll call the police.

41
00:03:26,661 --> 00:03:29,742
Bin, I'm in Beijing now.

42
00:03:29,742 --> 00:03:31,381
This has nothing to do with me.

43
00:03:31,381 --> 00:03:32,742
It was all Anna's idea.

44
00:03:32,742 --> 00:03:34,421
I couldn't stop her.

45
00:03:34,421 --> 00:03:37,002
She just wants to take Gao Yang away.

46
00:03:37,002 --> 00:03:38,502
Where are they now?

47
00:03:38,502 --> 00:03:40,342
They're probably in Linyang by now.

48
00:03:40,342 --> 00:03:41,821
I heard they're staying in Linyang tonight.

49
00:03:41,821 --> 00:03:43,222
They will return to Beijing tomorrow morning.

50
00:03:43,222 --> 00:03:45,041
Back to Beijing?

51
00:03:45,041 --> 00:03:47,582
How can Anna do that? Why didn't you stop your wife?

52
00:03:47,582 --> 00:03:51,242
You didn't stop your ex-wife and your son either.

53
00:03:51,242 --> 00:03:54,162
What a lame comment.

54
00:03:54,162 --> 00:03:55,481
Alright, Bin.

55
00:03:55,481 --> 00:03:56,782
You should call Anna yourself.

56
00:03:56,782 --> 00:04:00,222
Only if she's willing to answer it, Dude!

57
00:04:00,222 --> 00:04:01,502
Uncle Zhan, I'm Xiaowen.

58
00:04:01,502 --> 00:04:04,362
Can you tell me where she's staying tonight?

59
00:04:06,962 --> 00:04:09,202
Okay.

60
00:04:15,481 --> 00:04:16,421
- Sir!
- Sir!

61
00:04:16,421 --> 00:04:18,001
- Sir!
- Sir!

62
00:04:23,882 --> 00:04:25,202
Sir! Sir!

63
00:04:25,202 --> 00:04:27,553
Sir! Sir!

64
00:04:28,402 --> 00:04:32,171
- Why don't we go to the coach station?
- There's no coach at this hour.

65
00:04:33,822 --> 00:04:36,382
Sir! Sir!

66
00:04:37,722 --> 00:04:38,972
What are you doing? Are you feigning an accident?

67
00:04:38,972 --> 00:04:40,522
I'm sorry, Sir. Sir, I want to go to Linyang.

68
00:04:40,522 --> 00:04:42,202
I'm not taking passengers. My shift is over.

69
00:04:42,202 --> 00:04:44,242
- We'll pay you extra.
- No can do.

70
00:04:44,242 --> 00:04:46,698
Sir! Sir!

71
00:04:52,881 --> 00:04:54,288
Come with me.

72
00:04:59,422 --> 00:05:01,862
Dawei, open the door!

73
00:05:02,862 --> 00:05:04,821
Who is it? We're closed! Come back tomorrow.

74
00:05:04,821 --> 00:05:07,681
Dawei, I'm Mr. Gao! Open the door!

75
00:05:07,681 --> 00:05:09,696
Mr. Gao?

76
00:05:11,601 --> 00:05:12,982
Dawei, I have an emergency.

77
00:05:12,982 --> 00:05:14,877
Please lend me your car.

78
00:05:18,381 --> 00:05:19,782
Anna is so unreliable.

79
00:05:19,782 --> 00:05:21,622
How can she be a mother like that?

80
00:05:21,622 --> 00:05:23,582
How can she do something so absurd?

81
00:05:23,582 --> 00:05:26,121
Gao Yang is just the same. How old is he?

82
00:05:26,121 --> 00:05:29,221
How can he be abducted without a word?

83
00:05:29,221 --> 00:05:32,162
Gao Yang must have his reasons.

84
00:05:32,162 --> 00:05:36,082
Mr. Gao, stay calm when we get there.

85
00:05:36,082 --> 00:05:38,341
Don't start a fight.

86
00:05:40,001 --> 00:05:45,002
Xiaowen, I'm so sorry about this.

87
00:05:45,002 --> 00:05:46,742
You came here to study.

88
00:05:46,742 --> 00:05:49,182
We keep getting you into this monkey business.

89
00:05:49,182 --> 00:05:50,801
It's okay.

90
00:05:50,801 --> 00:05:52,542
Let's get Gao Yang back first.

91
00:05:52,542 --> 00:05:53,940
We're almost there.

92
00:05:53,940 --> 00:05:58,180
[Linyang: 80km, Beijing: 130km]

93
00:06:15,141 --> 00:06:17,161
Is this room okay?

94
00:06:17,161 --> 00:06:19,648
If you don't like it, we can change to another one.

95
00:06:21,261 --> 00:06:22,876
Are you hungry?

96
00:06:24,062 --> 00:06:26,703
Let's order something.

97
00:06:32,542 --> 00:06:36,102
Gao Yang, keep your temper in check.

98
00:06:36,102 --> 00:06:38,151
Go hungry then.

99
00:06:41,461 --> 00:06:44,102
Get some sleep soon. We're leaving tomorrow morning.

100
00:06:44,102 --> 00:06:48,662
When will you transfer the money you're donating to the hospital?

101
00:06:51,021 --> 00:06:53,109
Let's talk about that when we're in Beijing.

102
00:06:56,243 --> 00:07:02,390
[Episode 28: Once My Happiness Was Bigger Than the World]

103
00:07:40,261 --> 00:07:42,098
I'll go take a look.

104
00:07:57,141 --> 00:07:59,061
What's going on, Mr. Gao?

105
00:08:01,021 --> 00:08:02,996
I think the car broke down.

106
00:08:21,282 --> 00:08:23,285
Emergency rescue?

107
00:08:23,285 --> 00:08:26,102
Yes, my car broke down.

108
00:08:26,102 --> 00:08:28,082
Can you pick us up?

109
00:08:28,082 --> 00:08:30,381
We're about...

110
00:08:33,101 --> 00:08:36,962
50km away from Linyang. Yes.

111
00:08:40,422 --> 00:08:42,437
What did they say, Mr. Gao?

112
00:08:43,101 --> 00:08:49,241
The soonest they can come is tomorrow morning.

113
00:08:49,241 --> 00:08:51,022
Tomorrow morning?

114
00:08:51,022 --> 00:08:53,757
Gao Yang would be gone by tomorrow morning!

115
00:09:00,681 --> 00:09:02,862
It's too late.

116
00:09:05,501 --> 00:09:07,426
It's too late.

117
00:09:08,441 --> 00:09:10,341
It's too late.

118
00:09:10,921 --> 00:09:12,303
No,

119
00:09:17,302 --> 00:09:19,141
there has to be another way.

120
00:09:23,801 --> 00:09:25,363
There has to be another way.

121
00:09:26,942 --> 00:09:31,981
Mr. Gao, think of something else. Mr. Gao.

122
00:09:31,981 --> 00:09:33,661
I'm out of ideas.

123
00:09:59,321 --> 00:10:01,321
Xiaowen, where are you going?

124
00:10:01,321 --> 00:10:02,942
I'll run over there!
[Please do not imitate dangerous actions]

125
00:10:02,942 --> 00:10:04,581
It's so far away. How could you

126
00:10:04,581 --> 00:10:07,381
I'll get Gao Yang back!

127
00:10:10,729 --> 00:10:26,324
[Please do not imitate dangerous actions]

128
00:10:49,660 --> 00:10:53,850
[Linyang: 30km, Beijing: 80km]

129
00:11:05,740 --> 00:11:08,850
[Linyang: 10km, Beijing: 60km]

130
00:11:25,560 --> 00:11:28,382
Gao Yang, are you awake?

131
00:11:28,382 --> 00:11:30,141
It's time to go.

132
00:12:11,060 --> 00:12:12,732
Gao Yang!

133
00:12:17,220 --> 00:12:18,791
Gao Yang!

134
00:12:19,762 --> 00:12:21,457
Gao Yang!

135
00:12:25,841 --> 00:12:28,225
Stop the car! Stop the car now!

136
00:12:32,122 --> 00:12:33,801
Stop the car!

137
00:12:33,801 --> 00:12:36,131
Stop the car now!

138
00:12:36,131 --> 00:12:39,145
Stop the car! Do you want to die?

139
00:12:44,660 --> 00:12:46,440
Where are you going?

140
00:12:46,441 --> 00:12:48,561
You better think carefully.

141
00:13:20,801 --> 00:13:22,538
You can go now.

142
00:13:26,220 --> 00:13:28,382
Tell Gao Bin and the others

143
00:13:29,122 --> 00:13:30,868
that I'm going to Beijing.

144
00:13:37,682 --> 00:13:39,102
- Why?
- No reason.

145
00:13:39,102 --> 00:13:40,942
What's wrong with you, Gao Yang?

146
00:13:40,942 --> 00:13:44,581
Gao Yang, did you forget what you told your dad?

147
00:13:44,581 --> 00:13:47,082
Did you forget what you told me?

148
00:13:47,082 --> 00:13:49,662
Aren't you going to Beijing on your own account?

149
00:13:49,662 --> 00:13:51,861
Why did you lie to me?

150
00:13:57,260 --> 00:13:59,561
I treated you like family!

151
00:13:59,561 --> 00:14:01,861
What do you take me for?

152
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:19,922
Xiaowen, prepare for the exam!

153
00:14:19,922 --> 00:14:22,280
You have to get into the Beijing University of Technology!

154
00:14:29,701 --> 00:14:31,242
Gao Yang!

155
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:35,242
Gao Yang!

156
00:14:39,220 --> 00:14:41,155
Gao Yang!

157
00:15:29,580 --> 00:15:31,449
Stop the car, Sir!

158
00:15:35,282 --> 00:15:37,100
There's no parking here.

159
00:15:54,780 --> 00:15:56,455
Xiaowen.

160
00:16:15,762 --> 00:16:17,821
One,

161
00:16:18,961 --> 00:16:20,768
two,

162
00:16:21,482 --> 00:16:23,742
three...

163
00:16:23,742 --> 00:16:26,601
Keep jumping, Jin Doudou! Don't slack off.

164
00:16:26,601 --> 00:16:29,743
Sis, I can't do it anymore.

165
00:16:29,743 --> 00:16:33,242
That's why you have to practice. The standard is 120 per minute.

166
00:16:33,242 --> 00:16:34,522
Look at how chubby you are.

167
00:16:34,522 --> 00:16:37,062
If you don't qualify, Ms. Meng will surely scold you. Hurry up and practice.

168
00:16:37,062 --> 00:16:40,062
Sis, can you demonstrate it for me?

169
00:16:40,062 --> 00:16:41,875
Sure, give it to me.

170
00:16:44,482 --> 00:16:47,001
Stand back. Don't let it strike you.

171
00:16:47,501 --> 00:16:49,175
Watch this.

172
00:16:51,300 --> 00:16:52,461
Do you see that?

173
00:16:52,461 --> 00:16:56,342
Put the rope in front of you before you jump. Do you see that?

174
00:16:58,042 --> 00:17:00,981
This rope is too long. I'll shorten it for you.

175
00:17:07,730 --> 00:17:08,722
Go!

176
00:17:08,722 --> 00:17:09,762
Jin Doudou, what are you doing?

177
00:17:09,762 --> 00:17:11,321
♪ I have a little donkey ♪

178
00:17:11,321 --> 00:17:13,942
Who are you calling a donkey?

179
00:17:13,942 --> 00:17:16,701
I'll wear you out!

180
00:17:17,598 --> 00:17:21,118
Uncle Gao, Xiaowen, where did you go?

181
00:17:21,762 --> 00:17:23,702
Xiaowen, what happened?

182
00:17:23,702 --> 00:17:26,182
You don't look well.

183
00:17:26,922 --> 00:17:28,822
Where's Gao Yang?

184
00:17:37,180 --> 00:17:38,814
Beibei,

185
00:17:39,261 --> 00:17:41,010
Gao Yang...

186
00:17:42,780 --> 00:17:43,862
He went to Beijing.

187
00:17:43,862 --> 00:17:47,921
That's not possible. Didn't he say he didn't want to go to Beijing?

188
00:17:47,921 --> 00:17:49,889
It's real this time.

189
00:18:00,900 --> 00:18:04,021
Why did Gao Yang leave without a word?

190
00:18:06,762 --> 00:18:08,529
I don't know.

191
00:18:09,442 --> 00:18:12,642
He didn't even give us a heads up this time.

192
00:18:12,642 --> 00:18:14,882
Why do you think he did that?

193
00:18:15,561 --> 00:18:17,501
Is Gao Yang terminally ill?

194
00:18:17,501 --> 00:18:19,248
What are you saying?

195
00:18:19,248 --> 00:18:21,981
I mean, maybe he left because he's ill.

196
00:18:21,981 --> 00:18:25,962
Don't make fun of this, Xiaowen is so worried that he came down with a fever.

197
00:18:25,962 --> 00:18:28,421
Is Xiaowen better now?

198
00:18:29,340 --> 00:18:30,813
No.

199
00:18:30,813 --> 00:18:36,141
He still has it. He's exhausted from chasing after Gao Yang for 50km.

200
00:18:37,321 --> 00:18:38,301
Beibei,

201
00:18:38,301 --> 00:18:40,021
did you get in touch with Gao Yang?

202
00:18:40,021 --> 00:18:42,921
He won't answer my calls.

203
00:18:52,361 --> 00:18:54,086
Come on, Yang.

204
00:18:54,462 --> 00:18:55,881
Here's the fish.

205
00:18:55,881 --> 00:18:57,138
Put it here.

206
00:18:57,138 --> 00:18:58,682
This fish is really fresh.

207
00:18:58,682 --> 00:19:01,661
- Alright.
- Here, Yang. This is your favorite.

208
00:19:01,661 --> 00:19:05,962
Yang, from now on, this is your home.

209
00:19:05,962 --> 00:19:07,641
Don't see yourself as an outsider.

210
00:19:07,641 --> 00:19:09,102
- Eat this.
- Here.

211
00:19:09,102 --> 00:19:11,682
After you start school, the other classes are less important.

212
00:19:11,682 --> 00:19:13,961
Pay attention to the English class, okay?

213
00:19:15,942 --> 00:19:20,322
Zhan, maybe we should hire an English tutor for him.

214
00:19:20,322 --> 00:19:22,404
We should do that.

215
00:19:22,404 --> 00:19:24,282
Leave that to me.

216
00:19:24,282 --> 00:19:25,801
Okay.

217
00:19:25,801 --> 00:19:27,741
Yang, eat something.

218
00:19:28,522 --> 00:19:31,701
Gao Yang, eat your food.

219
00:19:32,700 --> 00:19:34,725
What's wrong with you now?

220
00:19:35,740 --> 00:19:39,002
Yang, you don't like these dishes?

221
00:19:39,002 --> 00:19:41,351
I'll ask the maid to make you some more.

222
00:19:50,202 --> 00:19:54,902
Gao Yang, do you have a problem with the dishes

223
00:19:54,902 --> 00:19:57,133
or do you have a problem with me?

224
00:19:58,061 --> 00:20:00,045
Did you transfer the money to the orphanage?

225
00:20:05,420 --> 00:20:08,662
I'm your mother. You can't even trust me?

226
00:20:08,662 --> 00:20:10,484
When are you making the transfer?

227
00:20:13,220 --> 00:20:15,282
I'll do that tomorrow.

228
00:20:15,282 --> 00:20:16,461
Can you eat now?

229
00:20:16,461 --> 00:20:18,066
Thank you, Mom.

230
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:54,182
Gao Yang, you came back?

231
00:20:54,182 --> 00:20:56,082
I'm always here.

232
00:20:59,282 --> 00:21:00,991
Drink the water.

233
00:21:04,380 --> 00:21:05,902
Gao Yang.

234
00:21:05,902 --> 00:21:07,724
Gao Yang!

235
00:21:07,724 --> 00:21:09,002
Gao Yang!

236
00:21:09,002 --> 00:21:10,539
Gao Yang!

237
00:21:22,139 --> 00:21:24,598
Hello? Zhan, I'm Gao Bin.

238
00:21:24,598 --> 00:21:26,035
Is it a good time to talk?

239
00:21:26,035 --> 00:21:28,398
Bin, it's not a good time.

240
00:21:28,398 --> 00:21:29,498
Don't hang up!

241
00:21:29,498 --> 00:21:32,817
Zhan, I'll call you elder brother, okay?

242
00:21:33,902 --> 00:21:35,801
I had a bad attitude last time.

243
00:21:35,801 --> 00:21:37,081
I apologize.

244
00:21:37,081 --> 00:21:38,762
I'm begging you.

245
00:21:38,762 --> 00:21:41,762
I don't know what's wrong with Gao Yang. Neither Anna nor Gao Yang would answer my call.

246
00:21:41,762 --> 00:21:43,161
You're the only one I can talk to.

247
00:21:43,161 --> 00:21:46,921
Bin, I really can't get involved in this.

248
00:21:46,921 --> 00:21:49,878
What if Anna suspects me?

249
00:21:49,878 --> 00:21:52,719
You should ask her yourself, okay?

250
00:21:53,762 --> 00:21:55,541
Xiaowen is sick.

251
00:21:55,541 --> 00:21:57,081
I can't leave.

252
00:21:57,081 --> 00:22:01,842
Did you know? Our car broke down while we chased after Gao Yang.

253
00:22:01,842 --> 00:22:05,199
Xiaowen ran over 50km to see Gao Yang.

254
00:22:05,199 --> 00:22:06,848
In the end,

255
00:22:07,660 --> 00:22:09,361
he didn't even get an explanation.

256
00:22:09,361 --> 00:22:12,061
I don't mind Gao Yang living with his mom,

257
00:22:12,061 --> 00:22:17,601
but Xiaowen and I don't even deserve an explanation?

258
00:22:17,601 --> 00:22:21,501
Is Gao Yang planning to cut off all ties with us?

259
00:22:22,182 --> 00:22:27,282
Chonghai, I raised Gao Yang for 18 years.

260
00:22:27,282 --> 00:22:31,461
Bin, Gao Yang isn't abandoning you.

261
00:22:31,461 --> 00:22:34,962
I've figured it out from the fragments I heard these days.

262
00:22:34,962 --> 00:22:37,342
Xiaowen's orphanage is about to close down.

263
00:22:37,342 --> 00:22:39,161
Anna donated some money.

264
00:22:39,161 --> 00:22:42,542
Gao Yang came to Beijing because of that.

265
00:23:07,700 --> 00:23:09,021
Dean.

266
00:23:09,021 --> 00:23:12,701
Xiaowen, what's wrong?

267
00:23:12,701 --> 00:23:14,422
Is our orphanage

268
00:23:14,422 --> 00:23:17,282
having trouble?

269
00:23:18,500 --> 00:23:20,581
You heard about it?

270
00:23:20,581 --> 00:23:22,002
It's okay.

271
00:23:22,002 --> 00:23:23,701
It's all in the past now.

272
00:23:23,701 --> 00:23:26,422
A nice person made a donation.

273
00:23:26,422 --> 00:23:29,382
Our orphanage will be able to stay open.

274
00:23:29,382 --> 00:23:31,221
You just prepare for your exam.

275
00:23:31,221 --> 00:23:34,062
Tell Mi Jia not to worry too.

276
00:23:34,962 --> 00:23:37,342
What's the name

277
00:23:37,342 --> 00:23:39,082
of that donator?

278
00:23:39,500 --> 00:23:41,640
It was a female boss from Beijing.

279
00:23:41,640 --> 00:23:43,260
Surnamed An.

280
00:23:43,260 --> 00:23:45,501
She's such a kind person.

281
00:24:25,078 --> 00:24:27,718
Meng, I don't know how to do this auxiliary line.

282
00:24:27,718 --> 00:24:29,518
Explain it to me.

283
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:34,522
Jia, is Xiaowen's birthday coming up?

284
00:24:35,780 --> 00:24:37,501
Let's celebrate it for him.

285
00:24:37,501 --> 00:24:39,441
That's right. He's going to be 18.

286
00:24:39,441 --> 00:24:42,941
Only once in our lives will we be young. We need to have a blast.

287
00:24:50,460 --> 00:24:52,301
What's wrong, Jia?

288
00:24:53,020 --> 00:24:57,401
I... I know Xiaowen pretty well.

289
00:24:57,401 --> 00:25:00,618
He never liked to celebrate his birthday since he was a child

290
00:25:00,618 --> 00:25:05,618
because birthdays are bad memories for him.

291
00:25:05,618 --> 00:25:10,141
Now that Gao Yang left, he must be in an even worse mood.

292
00:25:16,517 --> 00:25:19,101
That won't do. Life still goes on in Tieyuan without Gao Yang.

293
00:25:19,101 --> 00:25:22,422
From now on, the little sunshine of Tieyuan will be me, Jin Beibei!

294
00:25:23,500 --> 00:25:26,242
How do you want to celebrate it then? Do you have a plan?

295
00:25:26,242 --> 00:25:28,742
Let's surprise him like how you fooled me back then.

296
00:25:28,742 --> 00:25:31,881
We'll get a big sparkler and set it off in front of Xiaowen.

297
00:25:31,881 --> 00:25:36,721
Then, we'll say, "Surprise!" Are you surprised? Happy birthday, Xiaowen!

298
00:25:36,721 --> 00:25:38,195
How's that?

299
00:25:41,220 --> 00:25:42,658
What's wrong?

300
00:25:42,658 --> 00:25:45,018
You're not interested?

301
00:25:45,018 --> 00:25:46,622
Don't be like that.

302
00:25:46,622 --> 00:25:49,102
I know you're all upset about Gao Yang's departure.

303
00:25:49,102 --> 00:25:50,701
I'm upset too.

304
00:25:50,701 --> 00:25:53,021
I wish I can smash him into pieces!

305
00:25:53,021 --> 00:25:55,222
But what's the point of that?

306
00:25:57,998 --> 00:26:02,178
Gao Yang left because of the orphanage.

307
00:26:06,250 --> 00:26:07,950
The orphanage?

308
00:26:15,500 --> 00:26:21,242
No wonder he didn't answer my calls or return my texts.

309
00:26:21,242 --> 00:26:24,261
He's not even signing on to QQ anymore.

310
00:26:26,100 --> 00:26:31,861
I... I can't believe it was Gao Yang who helped the dean.

311
00:26:38,340 --> 00:26:40,461
Thank you, Everyone.

312
00:26:40,461 --> 00:26:42,892
You're still thinking about celebrating my birthday.

313
00:26:43,461 --> 00:26:45,354
Don't go through that trouble.

314
00:26:47,220 --> 00:26:49,142
Do you have any birthday wishes?

315
00:26:49,142 --> 00:26:51,618
We can help you achieve it.

316
00:26:51,618 --> 00:26:54,382
I just want to get in touch with Gao Yang now.

317
00:26:54,382 --> 00:26:56,635
How should we get in touch with him?

318
00:26:57,182 --> 00:26:59,686
Should we go see him in Beijing?

319
00:26:59,686 --> 00:27:01,541
He wants to avoid everyone now.

320
00:27:01,541 --> 00:27:06,042
Besides, Beijing is so big. How will we find him?

321
00:27:10,860 --> 00:27:14,161
Xiaowen, your birthday is coming up.

322
00:27:14,161 --> 00:27:15,981
You'll be 18 after that.

323
00:27:15,981 --> 00:27:17,541
You'll be an adult when you're 18, right?

324
00:27:17,541 --> 00:27:20,762
That's nonsense. Why are you so garrulous?

325
00:27:22,060 --> 00:27:23,902
I know, Xiaowen.

326
00:27:23,902 --> 00:27:27,161
I'll take you somewhere when you're an adult.

327
00:27:27,161 --> 00:27:28,618
It's amazing.

328
00:27:28,618 --> 00:27:30,497
What do you want to do?

329
00:27:33,740 --> 00:27:36,522
So, you meant an internet café?

330
00:27:36,981 --> 00:27:38,202
What else?

331
00:27:38,202 --> 00:27:39,928
What did you think?

332
00:27:42,758 --> 00:27:45,090
Why did you take Xiaowen to an internet café?

333
00:27:45,660 --> 00:27:48,222
Xiaowen, do you have QQ?

334
00:27:48,222 --> 00:27:49,042
No.

335
00:27:49,042 --> 00:27:51,161
Our orphanage doesn't have computers.

336
00:27:51,161 --> 00:27:53,921
Plus, our school won't let us use the internet.

337
00:27:54,598 --> 00:27:56,214
You're right.

338
00:27:56,895 --> 00:27:58,666
How about this?

339
00:27:58,666 --> 00:27:59,942
Use mine to leave him a message.

340
00:27:59,942 --> 00:28:02,422
He'll see it when he signs in.

341
00:28:02,422 --> 00:28:04,802
Which one is Gao Yang?

342
00:28:04,802 --> 00:28:07,902
Here he is, "Gone with the Wind"

343
00:28:09,700 --> 00:28:12,662
However, he hasn't signed in for a long time.

344
00:28:13,300 --> 00:28:17,102
Jiabao, can you apply for a QQ number for me?

345
00:28:17,102 --> 00:28:19,721
That'll work too. Wait a minute.

346
00:28:25,480 --> 00:28:27,449
Come up with a name

347
00:28:50,020 --> 00:28:52,982
After that, click friendship request.

348
00:29:05,660 --> 00:29:08,401
It's not responding.

349
00:29:08,958 --> 00:29:12,329
How about this, Jiabao? We'll sign into your account. He would surely appear if you tell him off.

350
00:29:12,329 --> 00:29:15,182
I already did. He won't reply.

351
00:29:16,700 --> 00:29:18,862
Why don't you change your ID to Wang Cailing?

352
00:29:18,862 --> 00:29:20,927
Why did you bring her up?

353
00:29:22,140 --> 00:29:24,949
Is one computer shared by all five of you?

354
00:29:30,820 --> 00:29:34,201
Maybe I'll stay and wait for him.

355
00:29:34,201 --> 00:29:36,042
You can go home first.

356
00:29:36,042 --> 00:29:36,781
But...

357
00:29:36,781 --> 00:29:39,742
Don't worry. I already learned how to use it.

358
00:29:39,742 --> 00:29:41,171
Alright.

359
00:29:41,847 --> 00:29:43,422
- Let's go.
- Happy birthday.

360
00:29:43,422 --> 00:29:44,701
Thank you.

361
00:29:44,701 --> 00:29:46,566
Happy birthday, Xiaowen.

362
00:29:46,566 --> 00:29:47,698
Thank you.

363
00:29:47,698 --> 00:29:49,505
Happy birthday.

364
00:29:50,178 --> 00:29:52,978
Boss, put that computer on my tab.

365
00:30:12,530 --> 00:30:14,758
March, 2005.

366
00:30:14,758 --> 00:30:16,767
Men are allowed to cry, but not allowed to be a coward.

367
00:30:16,767 --> 00:30:18,847
I must go to Beijing this time.

368
00:30:18,847 --> 00:30:22,682
Although I didn't succeed this time, I'll surely do it next time.

369
00:30:24,061 --> 00:30:28,081
Even if God himself shows up in Tieyuan, he would have to show me respect.

370
00:30:28,081 --> 00:30:32,681
Ye Xiaowen, do you think I can't handle you?

371
00:30:33,338 --> 00:30:35,648
Dong Dawei,

372
00:30:35,648 --> 00:30:37,342
don't be so arrogant.

373
00:30:37,342 --> 00:30:39,261
I have more people on my team now.

374
00:30:39,261 --> 00:30:41,501
Ye Xiaowen stands no nonsense.

375
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:45,582
Attention, all boys in the No.3 High School.

376
00:30:45,582 --> 00:30:47,942
Mi Jia is mine and Ye Xiaowen's sister.

377
00:30:47,942 --> 00:30:51,882
Keep your eyes away from her.

378
00:30:52,342 --> 00:30:55,602
What will be will be.

379
00:30:55,602 --> 00:30:58,282
No one is more reliable than yourself.

380
00:30:58,282 --> 00:31:00,262
I'll go to Beijing on my own.

381
00:31:04,322 --> 00:31:06,981
Everyone from the No.3 High School should have some team spirit.

382
00:31:06,981 --> 00:31:09,002
Come and cheer for them tomorrow, Everyone.

383
00:31:09,002 --> 00:31:11,692
Mi Jia and Xiaowen will both win first place for sure.

384
00:31:12,161 --> 00:31:13,822
Let the waves hit the shore.

385
00:31:13,822 --> 00:31:15,721
Leave the sea behind.

386
00:31:15,721 --> 00:31:22,582
My studying process is 80% mock exams and 70% the right amount of sleep.

387
00:31:22,582 --> 00:31:25,842
The days without my buddy is hard to get by.

388
00:31:27,261 --> 00:31:32,261
Although you are too strong to have a weakness, I can still protect you.

389
00:31:32,261 --> 00:31:35,301
Xiaowen, I'll watch over you.

390
00:31:35,301 --> 00:31:38,041
Look, my younger brother is so obedient.

391
00:31:38,041 --> 00:31:40,742
He'll be an adult in two months.

392
00:31:41,562 --> 00:31:45,142
I won't trade my happiness for the entire world.

393
00:31:45,142 --> 00:31:47,202
I hope you feel the same.

394
00:32:38,860 --> 00:32:41,242
Xiaowen, I'm home.

395
00:32:42,522 --> 00:32:44,558
We're having noodles today?

396
00:32:44,558 --> 00:32:47,141
Don't make any more dishes. Let's eat.

397
00:32:55,478 --> 00:32:57,617
Xiaowen,

398
00:32:57,617 --> 00:33:00,341
I'm sorry. I forgot about your birthday.

399
00:33:00,341 --> 00:33:02,681
I'll go buy a bigger cake. This one doesn't even have cream.

400
00:33:02,681 --> 00:33:04,021
It's alright, Mr. Gao.

401
00:33:04,021 --> 00:33:07,122
I made it myself. Try it.

402
00:33:17,740 --> 00:33:20,862
Xiaowen, you're 18 today.

403
00:33:20,862 --> 00:33:23,021
You're an adult now.

404
00:33:24,461 --> 00:33:26,161
Did you know?

405
00:33:26,161 --> 00:33:30,961
On this day eighteen years ago, I held you when you were born.

406
00:33:32,562 --> 00:33:36,661
You even misunderstood me because of that photo.

407
00:33:39,420 --> 00:33:41,223
I never imagined

408
00:33:42,660 --> 00:33:45,762
we would spend your 18th birthday together.

409
00:33:49,461 --> 00:33:51,101
Make a wish.

410
00:34:01,740 --> 00:34:06,242
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

411
00:34:07,042 --> 00:34:11,801
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

412
00:34:12,322 --> 00:34:17,741
♪ Happy birthday, Dear Xiaowen ♪

413
00:34:18,921 --> 00:34:26,322
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

414
00:34:48,280 --> 00:34:50,341
Happy birthday.

415
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:22,580
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

416
00:35:22,580 --> 00:35:29,845
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

417
00:35:29,845 --> 00:35:35,735
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

418
00:35:35,735 --> 00:35:41,875
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

419
00:35:41,875 --> 00:35:48,527
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

420
00:35:48,527 --> 00:35:54,167
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

421
00:35:54,167 --> 00:35:58,180
♫  To chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

422
00:35:58,180 --> 00:36:01,602
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

423
00:36:01,602 --> 00:36:04,897
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

424
00:36:04,897 --> 00:36:11,557
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

425
00:36:11,557 --> 00:36:14,868
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

426
00:36:14,868 --> 00:36:19,080
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

427
00:36:19,080 --> 00:36:22,800
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

428
00:36:22,800 --> 00:36:30,760
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫p
